Package co.cask.cdap.api

Interfaces for program and resource specifications, program lifecycle, runtime context and processors.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Processor Process with a Processor.
ProgramLifecycle<T extends RuntimeContext> Defines program lifecycle.
ProgramSpecification This interface provides for getting the name, class name, and description specifications of any type of program.
ResourceSpecification This interface provides specifications for memory in MB and the number of virtual cores.
RuntimeContext This interface represents a context for a processor or elements of a processor.
 

Class Summary
Resources Implementation of ResourceSpecification.
ResourceSpecification.Builder Class for building ResourceSpecification.
SingleRunnableApplication A simple TwillApplication that contains only one TwillRunnable.
 

Enum Summary
ResourceSpecification.SizeUnit Unit for specifying memory size.
 

Package co.cask.cdap.api Description

Interfaces for program and resource specifications, program lifecycle, runtime context and processors.
